&lt;p&gt;We have an opportunity for an Occupational Health Technician to join our busy Occupational Health Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will be supporting our OH Nurses to deliver our OH Service by undertaking clinical duties such asaudiometry, spirometry, vibration white finger and keystone eye screening tests. Also to perform clinical measurements such as height, weight, blood pressure, pulse, visual acuity and colour perception health screening as directed for required employees. To undertake phlebotomy as required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you require any further information about the role please email f.davies2@nhs.net&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
